<DocsLayout title="Getting Started" description="Installation, project structure, and quick start guide">
	<section>
		<h2>Installation</h2>
		<p>Rizzo CSS is built on Astro. To use it in your project:</p>
		<pre><code>{`# Clone or copy the project
git clone <repository-url>
cd rizzo-css

# Install dependencies
pnpm install`}</code></pre>
	</section>
	
